        Stumpy Enemys: Color: Orange, Heath: High, Speed: None, Damage: small


        3.
        Key Enemys: Color: Yellow, Heath: Low, Speed: High, Damage: None

        Note(Will
        run form threats, but might contain helpful items)


        4 Speedy Enemys:
        Color: Green, Heath: Low, Speed: High, Damage: Low


        5. Tank Enemys:
        Color: Blue, Heath: High, Speed: Low, Damage: High'
